{"tid":994660,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我地都係男子組，歡迎想放低心事嘅巴打","createTime":"2019-01-25T00:54:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-25T08:28:34.000Z","uid":61154,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"41798b5dd94ce03549ef12573bc19bd3fb7d5fe0","tid":994660,"uid":61154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T00:54:04.000Z","msg":"係時候開下ＰＯＳＴ。<br />\n<br />\n有時候，有啲說話唔知同邊個講，有啲情感唔知同邊個傾訴，有啲遺憾唔適合同異性分享。<br />\n<br />\n兩個幾月前開左一個谷，我地大家都係男子組，好多巴打都有自己有趣事、心事想放低。<br />\n<br />\n我地只係想重組男性力量，互相安慰，係而家呢個後現代情感觀複雜嘅社會，為大家開啟一個避風港。<br />\n<br />\n來吧，孩子，男人都需要眼淚，需要安慰，有我地係度，你可以盡情喊，盡情笑，齋呵唔鬧。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/FLcl-g_aL9Vt2YQiR1m8FQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FFLcl-g_aL9Vt2YQiR1m8FQ&d=4wHvwn0c8GG2%2BJennq%2Fg3L%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=d44efb1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/FLcl-g_aL9Vt2YQiR1m8FQ</a>"},{"pid":"8e315089685a09d30b0901cfc10a9c1208cf2e7d","tid":994660,"uid":61154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T00:57:59.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"9ac0323923c1672d9093c412cfba4d616c625eca","tid":994660,"uid":61154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T02:49:46.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"0eb9f2943aa83e33e310f0ac3d78f716e1e3ade3","tid":994660,"uid":144833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T02:54:04.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"f725571c648570e8678f5e0f0a47b911c071bb2c","tid":994660,"uid":61154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0eb9f2943aa83e33e310f0ac3d78f716e1e3ade3","tid":994660,"uid":144833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T02:54:04.000Z","msg":"推推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T03:01:27.000Z","msg":"人間有愛阿巴打"},{"pid":"2409bb5d616ca3998e2d5ac2bf10c84bdbad3b91","tid":994660,"uid":86762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T03:13:34.000Z","msg":"見住鍾意嘅女仔同其他男仔傾計傾得好開心 都幾心痛下<br />\n<br />\n(就啱啱發生